data.description: This spacious townhome includes 3 bedrooms, 3 full baths, and 2 half baths, along with hardwoods throughout the entire home, high ceilings, recessed lighting, 1-car garage, and quartz countertops. Two outdoor spaces perfect for pets. Whole-house water filtration system with a reverse osmosis drinking tap in the kitchen! Smart home features include a doorbell camera, smart lock, and learning thermostats on each floor. Newly remodeled master and guest bedroom closets! Stainless steel appliances and high-efficiency washer and dryer included!     The covered rooftop terrace is so cozy- ENJOY RAIN OR SHINE! Flex room w/ 1/2 bath off terrace great for office, media room or spare guest room. Lower level bedroom w/ full bath provides a perfect roommate plan!     The Row on Wylie is conveniently located near the Atlanta Beltline, Edgewood Retail District, Memorial Corridor, Inman Park, MARTA, E'wood Performing Arts, and Pullman Yards. Little 5 is only one mile away and Edgewood shopping even closer! Super hot and fast growing area! Get it while you can!    Closing Attorney is to be Ganek PC Midtown
